# Hello Life

This is a Life repo. The kernel is `./.life.core`.

    ./.life.core status            # current state
    ./.life.core explain <path>    # what governs this path
    ./.life.core check             # verify against reality
    ./.life.core help              # all commands

Run any command with the kernel from the repo root.
